{
  "stem": "1282.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the beginning, they still allowed him to come home every few months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm specifically speaking about our territory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was different everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I can only speak what was happening-- what was happening to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that pressure and those restrictions kept getting stronger and stronger to the point where they denied us to make a living at all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father dealt in, for example, in lumber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He bought large woods, areas of lumber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he sold it to people that cut the lumber down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was his sideline.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He made money in that since childhood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my mother was running the business, and the maids took care of the kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was more or less unheard of at that time, 50, 60 years ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was unheard of.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we were modern enough to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then when my-- they restricted us from doing business, they restricted my father from dealing in lumber, we literally had no way of making a living.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my father was always innovative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what he did, he come worked at the house which had several rooms where the store was, and where they-- what do you call it-- where we'd serve the wine-- it was like a tavern-- and built cages.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they did allow us to raise angora, angora rabbits.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we raised angora rabbits.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, from where we were to coming down to the stage where we had to raise angora rabbits to make a living, cut the wool and sell the wool, it was quite a come down.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fortunately, father had some money, and we did not suffer as badly because we had-- we had some money put aside for emergencies.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
